title: A Wilderness in Your Heart
description:
A Wilderness in Your Heart (2007)
Unrated  |  Video  |  85 min

A unique blend of 'Before Sunset,' 'My Dinner with Andre' and 'Lost Highway', Robin Dunn's first feature film "A Wilderness in Your Heart" explores the light and dark sides of passionate love, eros and thanatos.

Director: Robin Wyatt Dunn 
Writer: Robin Wyatt Dunn 
Stars: Robin Wyatt Dunn, Anna McConnell
